article.headline: Sacramento St. 77, N. Arizona 43
article.story: SACRAMENTO, Calif. -- Konner Veteto scored 24 points off the bench and grabbed seven rebounds as Sacramento State rolled to a 77-43 victory over Northern Arizona on Saturday night. Sacramento State (6-14, 1-8 Big Sky) earned its first conference win of the season as Jackson Carbajal scored 18 points, Dylan Garrity scored 11 points and handed out eight assists and Joe Eberhard grabbed eight rebounds. Northern Arizona (5-16, 1-8) got 13 points from Gabe Rogers and 11 points from James Douglas. Sacramento State had a 50-20 scoring advantage in the paint, had a 25-9 scoring advantage off turnovers and a 36-15 advantage off the bench.
